{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhoixtvmp880","created":1775727713425,"text":"需求工程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpaf103w0g0","created":1775805231092,"text":"需求开发（获分归雁）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpaf4j8yzc0","created":1775805238779,"text":"需求获取"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpaf89e38w0","created":1775805246890,"text":"需求分析"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpaikdpniw0","created":1775805508366,"text":"结构化分析（SA）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpake7db000","created":1775805651650,"text":"基本思想：自顶向下，逐步分解"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpakst4tgg0","created":1775805683441,"text":"分析模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpakuyoi7s0","created":1775805688130,"text":"核心：数据字典"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpal16x1sw0","created":1775805701688,"text":"数据模型（ER图）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpalcd4vy00","created":1775805726009,"text":"功能模型（数据流图）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpamck3gp40","created":1775805804794,"text":"基本符号"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpamf2atx40","created":1775805810248,"text":"数据流（标有名字的箭头）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpamlxfvkw0","created":1775805825192,"text":"加工/数据处理（圆圈）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpamtj8jww0","created":1775805841747,"text":"数据存储（直线段）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpamzj5s0w0","created":1775805854803,"text":"外部实体，比如数据源、数据终点（标有名字的方框）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpao7uzd0o0","created":1775805951297,"text":"与（*）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpaoa20tr40","created":1775805956076,"text":"或（+）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpaocwu1o80","created":1775805962293,"text":"异或（⊕）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpax21pq7c0","created":1775806643920,"text":"平衡原则"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpayekxczc0","created":1775806749568,"text":"父图与子图平衡"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpayn08aqo0","created":1775806767907,"text":"个数一致（两层图中的数据流个数一致）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpayog5ew80","created":1775806771047,"text":"方向一致（两层图中的数据流方向一致）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpb3l8rs4g0","created":1775807155891,"text":"子图内部平衡"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpb4a9kxsw0","created":1775807210360,"text":"没有黑洞（加工有输入无输出）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpb4jb6ktc0","created":1775807230047,"text":"没有奇迹（加工无输入有输出）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpb4pcejn40","created":1775807243182,"text":"没有灰洞（加工输入不足以产生输出）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpb5a425zk0","created":1775807288390,"text":"数据存储（必须既有读的数据流又有写的数据流）"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpb073kgkw0","created":1775806890009,"text":"注意"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpb0a38qrc0","created":1775806896520,"text":"数据存储要被外部实体使用必须要经过加工"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpalh0d2ds0","created":1775805736121,"text":"行为模型（状态转换图）"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpaiq408n40","created":1775805520839,"text":"面向对象分析（OOA）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpba01o1uo0","created":1775807658298,"text":"分析模型/对象模型（类图）（记忆：饭食组，聚关羽）","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpdp0twwwo0","created":1775814477688,"text":"关联","expandState":"expand","layout_right_offset":{"x":9,"y":221}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhrvm8pzjig0","created":1776068159664,"text":"逻辑上存在联系，比如学生和课程"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpdp2wbli80","created":1775814482188,"text":"依赖","layout_right_offset":{"x":13,"y":223}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhrvmfiwhnc0","created":1776068174474,"text":"临时使用的关系，用完即散"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpdp61ihg80","created":1775814489032,"text":"聚合","layout_right_offset":{"x":16,"y":53}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhrvkwzrl400","created":1776068055770,"text":"整体与部分，生命周期不同"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpdp8f1tug0","created":1775814494204,"text":"实现","layout_right_offset":{"x":2,"y":-101}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhrvjycwffc0","created":1776067980377,"text":"接口和实现"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpdp7n7xt40","created":1775814492521,"text":"组合","layout_right_offset":{"x":9,"y":-101}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhrvk9alasg0","created":1776068004182,"text":"整体与部分，“部分”与“整体”生命周期相同；例如汽车和发动机"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpdp415ay80","created":1775814484656,"text":"泛化","layout_right_offset":{"x":-6,"y":-252}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhrvjdnxhqg0","created":1776067935331,"text":"一般与特殊的关系，通常是父类和子类"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpba3ci9fc0","created":1775807665484,"text":"用例模型/功能模型（用例图）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpbb9x6k000","created":1775807758159,"text":"4个阶段（记忆：人合细调）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpbbbwg9fc0","created":1775807762468,"text":"识别参与者"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpd6tpkc340","created":1775813051634,"text":"其它系统"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpd6vl0xzs0","created":1775813055712,"text":"硬件设备"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpd6yoh3s80","created":1775813062451,"text":"时钟"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpbbdzy9ao0","created":1775807767034,"text":"合并需求获得用例"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpbbhzt6fs0","created":1775807775732,"text":"细化用例描述"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpbbl2shsw0","created":1775807782443,"text":"调整用例模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpd81uqimw0","created":1775813147724,"text":"包含关系"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpd9a4w23s0","created":1775813244117,"text":"多个用例的公共行为"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpd9hs96c80","created":1775813260767,"text":"<<include>> 虚线箭头"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpd9ohd2w80","created":1775813275346,"text":"比如“学习课程”和“课程测试”用例都需要“检测权限”"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpd84bs6ow0","created":1775813153108,"text":"扩展关系"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpdactqnbs0","created":1775813328337,"text":"一个基本用例和多个扩展用例"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpdbg0t8iw0","created":1775813413659,"text":"<<extend>> 虚线箭头"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpdbtkwcyg0","created":1775813443172,"text":"“课程测试”次数超过限额，需“充入学习币“，前者是基本用例，后者是扩展用例"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhpd86gcqag0","created":1775813157738,"text":"泛化关系"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhpdctklcmg0","created":1775813521517,"text":"多个用例有类似的行为，将共性抽象为父用例，其它为子用例，父子用例就是泛化关系"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpddd04f400","created":1775813563815,"text":"指向父用例的实线三角形箭头"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhpd